Once again , the indomitable peasant holds <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Poland</ENAMEX> 's future in his hands .
Until his labor can produce a profit in this dying and distorted system , even <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">Solidarity</ENAMEX> 's sympathetic new government wo n't win him over .
