At <ENAMEX TYPE="TIME">dawn</ENAMEX> on <ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">a cool day</ENAMEX> , <ENAMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">hundreds</ENAMEX> travel to the private market in <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Radzymin</ENAMEX> , a town not far from <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Warsaw</ENAMEX> , hauling pigs , cattle and sacks of feed that the state 's official buyers ca n't induce them to sell .
