In a crush of trucks and horse carts on the trodden field , <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Andrzej Latowski</ENAMEX> wrestles a screeching , overweight hog into the trunk of a private butcher 's <ENAMEX TYPE="NORP">Polish</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">Fiat</ENAMEX> .
