It wo n't be cheaper !
We sell direct ! ''
A heavy , kerchiefed woman runs a handful through her fingers , and counts him out a pile of zlotys .
`` Country people breed pigs , '' says Mr. <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Chojnowski</ENAMEX> , leaning against the back of his truck .
