The <ENAMEX TYPE="NORP">Poles</ENAMEX> have had it all along .
<ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Poland</ENAMEX> 's <ENAMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">2.7 million</ENAMEX> small private farms cover <ENAMEX TYPE="PERCENT">76 %</ENAMEX> of its arable land .
