Like <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">the Roman Catholic Church</ENAMEX> , the <ENAMEX TYPE="NORP">Polish</ENAMEX> peasant is a pillar of the nation .
Try as they might , the <ENAMEX TYPE="NORP">Communists</ENAMEX> could neither replace nor break him .
And they did try .
<ENAMEX TYPE="QUANTITY">A few miles</ENAMEX> past <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Radzymin</ENAMEX> , a dirt road narrows to a track of sand and leads into <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Zalubice</ENAMEX> , a village of tumbledown farms .
