In his <ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">lifetime</ENAMEX> , <ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">47 years</ENAMEX> , the <ENAMEX TYPE="NORP">Communists</ENAMEX> brought electricity to his village and piped in drinking water from the reservoir .
