Grain , milk and meat come next .
A private challenge to the monolithic tractor industry will take more time and money than <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Poland</ENAMEX> can spare , although a smokehouse or a local dairy can spring up fast .
<ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Poland</ENAMEX> makes no machinery for a plant on that scale .
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">Solidarity</ENAMEX> wants it from the West .
